p": 1637577368, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008157, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 工资也算  只要这价格跟他的劳动价值一致就行", "timestamp": 1637577594, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008189, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008157, "tag": null, "text": "事实上都是付的工资小于他劳动带来的价值  只要老板盈利了", "timestamp": 1637577651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008114, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 懂？", "timestamp": 1637577668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008195, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008183, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: dz说只要存在雇佣关系就是剥削！钱给够也是剥削！", "timestamp": 1637577682, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008200, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008189, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 那你说这个工资应该咋定？", "timestamp": 1637577707, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008215, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008195, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 。。。  特指资本主义下的雇佣劳动吧", "timestamp": 1637577804, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008223, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008189, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 现在就是想招一个保洁员，本来老板和保洁员已经达成一致要来上班了，现在你说老板给少了，那你说说他劳动带来的价值应该是多少？依据是什么？", "timestamp": 1637577864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008228, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008195, "tag": null, "text": "你懂就行  要是有个大单子要一百件产品  我干不过来雇你干活  你做了五十件  我就分你五十件的利润  这也没剥削", "timestamp": 1637577888, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008236, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008195, "tag": null, "text": "不过一般人都会少分你钱  所以你的部分劳动价值被无偿占有了", "timestamp": 1637577943, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008238, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008228, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 你既然是一个理论，应该适用于一切经济活动。不是说举一个例子，而是要能解释各种各样的经济活动", "timestamp": 1637577975, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008247, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008236, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 你说分少了，那到底应该加多少？依据是什么？", "timestamp": 1637578025, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008261, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008247, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: https://www.zhihu.com/question/61934560/answer/2029337601", "timestamp": 1637578111, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008247, "tag": null, "text": "自己看好吧  不想多费口舌了  浪费时间", "timestamp": 1637578133, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008278, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008247, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 剥削指以占有生产资料为基础的购买劳动力的行为，最终会导致工人所创造的价值中的一部分最终合法地被资本家占有的行为", "timestamp": 1637578292, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008288, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008247, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不管发多少工资，只要购买了劳动力，导致工人创造的价值中的一部分被资本家占有就是剥削。", "timestamp": 1637578397, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008312, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008223, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 老板给保洁员一定的工资，这个工资是购买了保洁员比如说每天12个小时的劳动力。而保洁员在这12个小时里创造的价值按法律来讲是归公司所有。后者就是剥削。", "timestamp": 1637578636, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008324, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008266, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 你有举了一个厨师作为服务业者的例子，但还是没有告诉我到底应该为这一个保洁员支付多少钱才是合理的？", "timestamp": 1637578732, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008337, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008312, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我想知道老板应该为一个保洁员定多少钱？如何定量的描述这个不剥削的工资应该是多少？", "timestamp": 1637578861, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008355, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008337, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 工资是劳动力的价值，是由市场上的供给和需求的关系来决定的。", "timestamp": 1637578977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008359, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008337, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你所谓的“不剥削的工资”指的是什么？", "timestamp": 1637579006, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008364, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008355, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我现在就是按照市场价值支付的呀，如果我开的价格比市场价格低，不会有人来呀", "timestamp": 1637579072, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008370, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008364, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 没问题啊", "timestamp": 1637579109, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008359, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 是说你认为现在保洁员领到的价格不合理，是老板剥削了他。那老板应该为他加多少钱，就不算剥削了？", "timestamp": 1637579141, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008381, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008359, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 一眼假，没学过马原吗，价值量与市场供需无关，仅有抽象劳动决定", "timestamp": 1637579159, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008383, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008377, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不管发多少工资，只要购买了劳动力，导致工人创造的价值中的一部分被资本家占有就是剥削。", "timestamp": 1637579166, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008385, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008381, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯嗯 你说得对，我写的不合理了", "timestamp": 1637579203, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008395, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008383, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 不管老板发多少，都是剥削？怎么量化一个保洁员创造的价值？", "timestamp": 1637579294, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008404, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008395, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 如何衡量价值，这些问题马克思都论述过😅西方经济学也论述过", "timestamp": 1637579350, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008411, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008395, "tag": null, "text": "不如去看看劳动价值论，也没必要在这争", "timestamp": 1637579398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008415, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008404, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 老板现在按照一个市场价值成交了，然后你说这个价格不合理。于是我就想知道多少就合理了？", "timestamp": 1637579432, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008395, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 老板按照市场价值交易的不是保洁员创造的价值，而是保洁员每天12个小时的劳动力", "timestamp": 1637579509, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008434, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008411, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 没看过劳动价值论的，就不能当老板？也不能当保洁员？", "timestamp": 1637579559, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008437, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008415, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 马克思研究的主要就是这个问题。要求按价值量分配就是对资本宣战", "timestamp": 1637579570, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008444, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008415, "tag": null, "text": "现实生活中当然完全不按劳动价值论那套来分配", "timestamp": 1637579633, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008445, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008424, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 这一个保洁员创造的价值是怎么量化的得到的呢？", "timestamp": 1637579639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008451, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008444, "tag": null, "text": " 所以大家既按照西方经济学效用价值那套思路在生活在讨论，又口口声声剥削真是😅", "timestamp": 1637579744, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008459, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008451, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 没有效用价值论吧", "timestamp": 1637579864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008460, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008459, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: ？", "timestamp": 1637579882, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008466, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008445, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 比如说一个没有打扫的写字楼和请一个保洁员来打扫的写字楼两个的租金差？", "timestamp": 1637579920, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008476, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这样就像连宣战纲领宣战目标都不知道，也整天喊杀杀杀", "timestamp": 1637580022, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008492, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008466, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 租金差a=请1个保洁员的写字楼的租金-请0个保洁员来打扫的写字楼租金", "timestamp": 1637580154, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008495, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008492, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 租金差b=请n+1个保洁员的写字楼的租金-请n个保洁员来打扫的写字楼租金", "timestamp": 1637580185, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008496, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008460, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 描述供给和需求并不需要引入效用吧，当然我前面说价值由需求和供给决定肯定是不对的", "timestamp": 1637580195, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008500, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008495, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 这下边际效用了", "timestamp": 1637580225, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008495, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 当发现租金差a与租金差b不想等时，应该以哪个租金差来量化一个保洁员创造的价值？", "timestamp": 1637580272, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008508, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008492, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: a不等于b，是怎么解释的来着我学得不太好", "timestamp": 1637580312, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008510, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008504, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 哎呀，你居然提问我，我晚点去查查经济学的书", "timestamp": 1637580341, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008521, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008504, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我没记错应该是a大于b吧", "timestamp": 1637580482, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3008539, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008521, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 按照边际效应，a理论上应该大于b", "timestamp": 1637580592, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009039, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "看开头第一句就在猜该不会是未明子那个视频", "timestamp": 1637584638, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009511, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008539, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 应该是（请n个保洁员来打扫的写字楼租金-请0个保洁员来打扫的写字楼租金）/n", "timestamp": 1637588114, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009591, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3008451, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 好。所以按照这个价格支付保洁员工资就可以了？", "timestamp": 1637588784, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009601, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009591, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可以什么？", "timestamp": 1637588846, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009617, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009601, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 就可以合理了？是一个对保洁员公平的工资？", "timestamp": 1637589004, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009625, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009617, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我没有讨论合理不合理吧", "timestamp": 1637589121, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009635, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009617, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 当你说“合理”“公平”的时候，你按什么来衡量呢？", "timestamp": 1637589213, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009653, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009625, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 之前说按照市场价格确定的工资是不合理的，存在剥削，因为你说这个价格是购买的劳动力，而不是保洁员创造的价值。于是我就问应该变到多少就合理了？应该怎么去量化这个值？", "timestamp": 1637589399, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009660, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009653, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我只是说存在剥削，我没有说过工资不合理", "timestamp": 1637589432, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009685, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009660, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 目前这个工资存在剥削。于是现在希望提高工资直至抹平这个剥削，那么应该提高多少呢？", "timestamp": 1637589668, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009793, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009685, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我的答案是不可能。有工资就有剥削，否则就不叫工资，叫慈善。", "timestamp": 1637590549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009808, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009793, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 所以结论还是说，要想不存在剥削，就不能雇佣保洁员？", "timestamp": 1637590629, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009825, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009808, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 反过来也对，不雇佣就不存在剥削", "timestamp": 1637590704, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009852, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009825, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 所以如果想要建立起一个没有剥削的社会，就需要禁止一切雇佣关系？", "timestamp": 1637590836, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009858, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009852, "tag": null, "text": "不谈雇佣，垄断交易是不是剥削", "timestamp": 1637590873, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009852, "tag": null, "text": "买卖器官是不是剥削", "timestamp": 1637590910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009883, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009852, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你一定要这么想也没大错，但我的想法是当雇佣关系消失之后，没有剥削的社会就有可能到来。", "timestamp": 1637591029, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009889, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009858, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 垄断交易的商品和买卖的器官都需要劳动力吧，那跟雇佣没有太大差别？我觉得", "timestamp": 1637591082, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009895, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009858, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 当然垄断我还不是很懂啦，我主要还是说的竞争的市场。", "timestamp": 1637591128, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009883, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 那么在一个没有剥削的社会里，不允许有雇佣关系，这时如果想为某所大学建造并投入使用一栋新宿舍楼，应该如何开展呢？", "timestamp": 1637591461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009954, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009939, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 哎所以我觉得你用这个“禁止”“不允许”这个词就很奇怪，好像有一个上帝允许和不允许一样", "timestamp": 1637591538, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009964, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009954, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 或者把“不允许有”换成“没有”", "timestamp": 1637591595, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009974, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009939, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那现在的社会里，这个问题怎么解决的？雇佣关系起到了什么作用呢？", "timestamp": 1637591645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009987, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009939, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 首先是招标，然后企业竞标，价低者得，然后企业组织工人来盖楼，我猜是这样的吧？", "timestamp": 1637591703, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3009994, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009987, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 如果没有雇佣关系，那事情其实也没怎么变呀，只不过组织者可能由企业变成了工会呗", "timestamp": 1637591746, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009974, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 现在的做法是，资方出钱，按照市场价格，雇佣一些建筑工人，工人进行生产建设，并领取工资。", "timestamp": 1637591794, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010014, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010006, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对，说白了就是企业组织工人干活，组织方式是雇佣制度", "timestamp": 1637591839, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010015, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3009994, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 问题是你说只要有雇佣关系，有工资发生，就产生了剥削？", "timestamp": 1637591850, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010019, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010006, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 以前是皇帝征徭役，再以前是奴隶主鞭笞奴隶，雇佣制度显然不是唯一的方式嘛", "timestamp": 1637591884, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010024, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010015, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对啊 怎么啦", "timestamp": 1637591900, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010030, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010015, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 盖大楼重要的是将工人组织起来，在过去有很多组织方式，雇佣的、徭役的、奴隶的，在未来也会有新的组织方式", "timestamp": 1637591970, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010031, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010024, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 对，所以说就不能通过发工资这种雇佣的形式来招建筑工人了？", "timestamp": 1637591974, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010019, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 你刚才提到了新的组织方式是由工会来组织？", "timestamp": 1637592032, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010037, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010031, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 哎呀不要说“不能”，又把上帝搬出来了，应该说没有这种方式，就好像现代社会也没有买奴隶这种方式来盖楼了呀", "timestamp": 1637592035, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010041, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010036, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 嗯这个是我个人觉得，工会有可能可以起到这个作用，你觉得呢？", "timestamp": 1637592060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010047, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010036, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 目前是工人受到工资吸引来应聘加入到这个项目的，那工会是如何使得工人愿意投入到这个项目中的呢？", "timestamp": 1637592116, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010048, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010047, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 这就是一个很深刻的问题了", "timestamp": 1637592137, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010053, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010047, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 为什么工人会受到工资的吸引呢？", "timestamp": 1637592156, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010063, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010047, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 如果在奴隶社会，奴隶是不会受到钞票的吸引的，因为钞票对他们来说就是破纸", "timestamp": 1637592190, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010067, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010047, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那也就是说，工人受到工资的吸引是有一定的历史和社会条件的", "timestamp": 1637592225, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010083, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010047, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那么在未来，工人还会不会受到钞票的吸引呢，很可能不会了，因为钞票起作用的历史和社会条件已经改变了", "timestamp": 1637592317, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010084, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010047, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 但我觉得，有一样东西是不变的，那就是这项工作如果对工人有利，工人是会去做的", "timestamp": 1637592349, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010085, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010053, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 因为工资是0元/月就不会有人来，工资是1000元/月也不会有人来，工资是2000元/月恐怕也不会有人来，以此类推，直到达到某一个价格后才能招到工人。这里唯一变化的因素是工资。", "timestamp": 1637592353, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010096, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010084, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 这个“有利因素”，可以量化吗？", "timestamp": 1637592419, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010100, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010096, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我还不懂得怎么量化，抱歉", "timestamp": 1637592439, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010109, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010085, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 工资不是唯一的变化因素，历史上还没有出现工资的时候，人类已经在盖楼了。", "timestamp": 1637592494, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010100, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 现在需要招募工人，工人为什么愿意来你这个项目工作？需要告诉工人他们通过参加这个工程具体能得到什么，不能只告诉工人说参加这个项目对他们“有利”吧？", "timestamp": 1637592644, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010132, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 确实啊，你说得很有道理。不过这个应该我来问你啊，是你说要为某所大学建造并投入使用一栋新宿舍楼的，你为啥要搞这个项目？", "timestamp": 1637592694, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010167, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010109, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 那么在现代的这样一个时代，为了要建成没有剥削的社会，你说要摒弃工资和雇佣，可以，可是你也需要提出应该要怎么样吧", "timestamp": 1637592861, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010141, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 搞这个项目的原因是为了满足学校新增学生的住宿需求", "timestamp": 1637592953, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010192, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010167, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不是，我的意思是，你自己都不明白这个项目对大家有什么好处，工人们当然也不明白了，这个项目就没必要搞了，如果你自己明白这个项目对大家有好处，大家也不比你蠢，那当然也都明白有好处了", "timestamp": 1637593024, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010208, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010187, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 学校扩招了，新学生需要新的宿舍楼，所以启动了这个项目。这个理由有什么不合理的吗？", "timestamp": 1637593133, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010216, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010208, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 如果合理就开工啊", "timestamp": 1637593180, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010221, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010192, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 对学生有好处，对学校有好处。可是人家建筑工人为什么要来工作？", "timestamp": 1637593217, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010228, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010221, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那就是不合理咯", "timestamp": 1637593251, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010233, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010221, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 问题就在于你为什么觉得学校把学生培养好了对工人没好处", "timestamp": 1637593271, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010237, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010221, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 而且这里只有我和你两个人，还不涉及民主决策的问题呢", "timestamp": 1637593300, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010240, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010228, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 在一个没有剥削的社会中，学校新建宿舍楼是不合理的？", "timestamp": 1637593330, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010249, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010221, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 现在清华每年花那么多国家的钱，也没有那么多人说不合理吧", "timestamp": 1637593366, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010254, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010240, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你自己觉得不合理的，不是我的判断！", "timestamp": 1637593384, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010258, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010233, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 不是我觉得有没有好处，而是你得说服工人们，让他们觉得有好处", "timestamp": 1637593394, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010267, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010258, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 要么就是你蠢，说不清楚，要么就是工人比你还蠢，你都理解了里面的好处，工人却不能理解", "timestamp": 1637593452, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010271, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010258, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你得说服建筑工人，他们为什么今天不在家躺着，而是要来上班参加这个项目的建设？", "timestamp": 1637593491, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010278, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010271, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我笑了，那你为什么不在家躺着，要来组织这个建设", "timestamp": 1637593543, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010284, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010267, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我是校长，我想扩招", "timestamp": 1637593592, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010290, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010284, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 为啥要扩招", "timestamp": 1637593612, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010267, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我也希望工人来上班，可是我不能剥削他们，所以我不能与他们建立雇佣关系", "timestamp": 1637593646, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010305, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010298, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 没让你建立雇佣关系啊", "timestamp": 1637593677, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010311, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010290, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 因为我想响应国家强基计划的号召，培养更多学生，这个理由可以吗？", "timestamp": 1637593748, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010322, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010311, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我觉得很可以啊，这对工人不是挺有好处的嘛", "timestamp": 1637593799, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010337, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010305, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 如果你是工人，听完我的建设理由，你就会来了？", "timestamp": 1637593866, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010353, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010337, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 当然有可能啊", "timestamp": 1637593932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010359, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010337, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你对比现实，现在为什么给工人一叠钞票他们就会来呢", "timestamp": 1637593962, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010369, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010337, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 因为这叠钞票对他们有好处啊，这需要你说服吗？这是他们天生就懂得的吗？都不是啊，是经过了历史的发展以及他们自己的社会生活之后才会懂得的", "timestamp": 1637594036, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010419, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010337, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那么放在你的情景里，你觉得培养更多学生是有好处的事情，这是你天生就懂得的吗？这是你经过教育以及社会生活和实践之后懂得的呀", "timestamp": 1637594295, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010337, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 假如你穿越到2000年前，给一个农民一叠厚厚的百元大钞，让他帮你干活，他只会觉得你是个傻子", "timestamp": 1637594458, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010446, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010369, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 你提到“当然有可能啊”，那么如何保证一批人也会和你保持一样的想法，不需要工资的激励，只因为建成这个项目对其他学生有利，就主动愿意来投入到这个项目中呢？", "timestamp": 1637594480, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010449, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010446, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那你不妨想想，现代社会是如何保证大家对货币保持基本一样的想法的呢？", "timestamp": 1637594525, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010453, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010419, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 你想怎么“教育”大家，从而让每个人都培养起这种“新理念”呢？", "timestamp": 1637594556, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010463, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010446, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 既然现代社会让大家对货币这种比土地、比粮食更抽象的东西保持基本一样的想法，那么未来很有可能大家会对更抽象的东西保持同样的想法", "timestamp": 1637594596, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010479, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010453, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不需要我来教育，也不需要上帝来教育，大家在不断的培养新理念", "timestamp": 1637594720, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3010486, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010453, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 在过去，这个信仰是土地，后来这个信仰变成了金银，再后来单纯金银已经不行了，大家要更抽象的货币，再后来，货币也要贬值了，房地产、金融产品又成了新理念", "timestamp": 1637594811, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3011502, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有这时间不如去翻一下资本论，我觉得里面讲得挺清楚了", "timestamp": 1637600663, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3011756, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "eve宛如一个傻子 给我笑疯了 alice还是不要扶贫了", "timestamp": 1637602958, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3012550, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3010486, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: “那么未来很有可能大家会对更抽象的东西保持同样的想法”。所以这个“更抽象”的“新理念”是什么？铁拳吗？", "timestamp": 1637631802, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3012887, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 未小将😓😓😓这人早都臭了", "timestamp": 1637634643, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3012888, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3011756, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 说反了吧", "timestamp": 1637634649, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3016931, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "球球别推这个nt未名子了，随便问问舍友也知道996和666哪个生产效率更高好吗？", "timestamp": 1637669262, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3018583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3011756, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 后面没有看，但开头明显ALICE不懂马原\n可是学马原不能应用在现实生活中，只会空洞的摆理论又有什么用呢？还是会被显示驳倒", "timestamp": 1637682050, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3021637, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3012550, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 你对“铁拳”的理解是什么？", "timestamp": 1637731448, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3021810, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3021637, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 就是大家对“铁拳”的理解。另外请正面回答什么是“新理念”，不要反问。", "timestamp": 1637732910, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3021879, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3021810, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 那大家对“铁拳”的理解是什么？", "timestamp": 1637733505, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3021885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3021810, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: “新理念”就是跟过去不同的理念，我也不知道是啥，反正不再是货币了。", "timestamp": 1637733542, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3021942, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3021810, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 如果你要跟Alice一样批评我没有提出具体可行的做法，没有“为未来的食堂开出调味单”，那没必要，我没说过我要消灭剥削，是Alice提出来要消灭剥削的", "timestamp": 1637733972, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3021960, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3021942, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我只是说，货币和雇佣制度并不是人类社会发展到绝对的最后的形式，离开了这两样东西，未来的人类社会一定发展不好，那我觉得这只是一厢情愿。", "timestamp": 1637734175, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3026056, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3021960, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 货币和雇佣关系还真有可能是绝对的最后的形式。比如只要满足“资源不是充足的”，“人与人需求不相同”等非常基础的假设，有可能能证明出这样的结论。Isabella不是研究社会学的同学，不知道这个问题的答案。既然Eve claim它一定不是“人类社会发展的绝对的最后的形式”，请给出证明或参考文献。但看到Eve目前和其他人的讨论，并没有给出这样的证明，而是一直在反驳Alice等人对另一个命题的证明，即反驳“货币和雇佣关系是目前最好的方案”。而这两个命题之间没有逻辑关系。", "timestamp": 1637769644, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3026210, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3026056, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 我没有反驳过“货币和雇佣关系是目前最好的方案”", "timestamp": 1637770323, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3026236, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3026056, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella:  只要满足“资源不是充足的”，“人与人需求不相同”等非常基础的假设，这些假设就不一定是永恒存在的", "timestamp": 1637770437, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3026242, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3026056, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 如果不能证明一样事物可以永恒存在，我一般都默认不能", "timestamp": 1637770467, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3026308, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3026056, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 人类社会长期同样满足“资源不是充足的”，“人与人需求不相同”等假设，但是出现货币的历史长度在人类的历史中实在是短得不能再短的一截，我虽然没法证明，但我难以置信这是绝对的最后的形式", "timestamp": 1637770879, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3027502, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3026308, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: Isabella认为如果希望得出可以指导当下社会生活的规律，有很多基本假设是不能脱离的。原因如下：人类的出现相对于地球的寿命也是“短得不能在短的一截”，如果脱离了这些基本假设去讨论，可能已经不是在讨论人类社会了。正如人类社会的理念不能指导几十亿年前的细菌的生活，未来的“新理念”也不能拿来指导现在的人类生活。", "timestamp": 1637801311, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3028039, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3027502, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 我没有拿新理念来指导现在的人类生活", "timestamp": 1637807366, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3028041, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3028039, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 新理念只能指导新生活", "timestamp": 1637807385, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3028145, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3027502, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 没有脱离你的基本假设，人类社会长期满足“资源不是充足的”，“人与人需求不相同”等假设，但是长期没有货币和雇佣制度", "timestamp": 1637808078, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3028162, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3028145, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 按你的说法，“资源不是充足的”，“人与人需求不相同”等假设只是货币和雇佣制度的必要条件而不是充分条件", "timestamp": 1637808155, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3028211, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3027502, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 如果要给一些假设证明货币和雇佣制度是在现在的条件下是最优的，那还有可能。想要证明它在未来永远是最优的，那是一厢情愿。", "timestamp": 1637808395, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 3028225, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 569816, "reply_to": 3028211, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 人类的出现相对于地球的寿命也是“短得不能在短的一截”，所以我们头脑中所理解的“人类”相对于地球并不一定能永恒持续下去。出现货币的历史长度在人类社会的历史中是短得不能再短的一截，所以我们头脑中所理解的货币相对于人类社会并不一定能永恒持续下去。这个逻辑是一样的。", "timestamp": 1637808527, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 39, "pid": 569816, "reply": 165, "tag": null, "text": "看到这个视频觉得有点道理，其实996不是剥削，雇佣关系产生的那一刻已经就在剥削了，996只是为了更好的支配你奴化你。\n\nhttps://b23.tv/Xqj5ZfN\n\n666生产效率更高，选用996不是为了效率，而是为了占用你的无用时间，使人奴役人，不在乎你的效率高低。\n晚9:6-9点是公关饭局商务时间，促成成交的时间，让你加班，减少你的社交，无形的削弱了竞争力。使你自降一格，主动成为依附他的人，\n早9:管理人员公关宿醉第二天起的晚，9点便于管理。而且可以占用你更多的通勤时间。\n周六加班而不是任选一天:甲方周五下班后到周六是可以放松一下，交流促成成交的时间，周日他们是留给家人的。技术人员是可以换，但是位置资源是有限的​。", "timestamp": 1637576793, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1637808526, "url": "", "vote": {}}}